[SN]TITLE[SN]
Tom Thorpe: Bradford City sign Rotherham United defender on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Bradford City have signed Rotherham United defender Tom Thorpe on loan until the end of the season.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Thorpe, 23, has made seven appearances for the Millers this season, but last featured in the 5-2 defeat by Ipswich on 7 November.
The former Manchester United trainee could make his Bradford debut against Millwall on Saturday.
The Bantams are currently seventh in League One, outside the play-offs on goal difference.
